content: standujar: Merged 4 PRs this month, including significant work on OpenAI plugin model usage events (#4438, +2409/-3824 lines) and fixing JSON serialization in PGLite (#4458, +2042/-2710 lines). Created 4 issues related to API functionality and logging, with 3 of them subsequently closed. Contributed to the codebase with a focus on bug fixes, removing more code than adding (+335/-3606 lines total) across 10 commits, while also participating in the review process with 2 reviews and 14 comments across PRs and issues.
